#. <section class="sutta" id="sn1.41"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn1.41:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 1"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 1"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn1.41:0.2"
msgid "5. Ādittavagga"
msgstr "5. On Fire"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn1.41:0.3"
msgid "41. Ādittasutta"
msgstr "41. On Fire"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.65"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.41:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "sn1.41:1.2"
msgid ""
"ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

msgctxt "sn1.41:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho aññatarā devatā abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇā kevalakappaṃ "
"jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ "
"abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi."
msgstr ""
"Then, late at night, a glorious deity, lighting up the entire Jeta’s Grove, "
"went up to the Buddha, bowed, stood to one side,"

msgctxt "sn1.41:1.4"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho sā devatā bhagavato santike imā gāthāyo abhāsi:"
msgstr "and recited these verses in the Buddha’s presence:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.41:2.1"
msgid "“Ādittasmiṃ agārasmiṃ,"
msgstr "“When your house is on fire,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.41:2.2"
msgid "yaṃ nīharati bhājanaṃ;"
msgstr "you rescue the pot"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.41:2.3"
msgid "Taṃ tassa hoti atthāya,"
msgstr "that’s useful,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.41:2.4"
msgid "no ca yaṃ tattha ḍayhati."
msgstr "not the one that’s burnt."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.41:3.1"
msgid "Evaṃ ādittako loko,"
msgstr "And as the world is on fire"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.41:3.2"
msgid "jarāya maraṇena ca;"
msgstr "with old age and death,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.41:3.3"
msgid "Nīharetheva dānena,"
msgstr "you should rescue by giving,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.41:3.4"
msgid "dinnaṃ hoti sunīhataṃ."
msgstr "for what’s given is rescued."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.32"></a>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.66"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.41:4.1"
msgid "Dinnaṃ sukhaphalaṃ hoti,"
msgstr "What’s given has happiness as its fruit,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.41:4.2"
msgid "nādinnaṃ hoti taṃ tathā;"
msgstr "but not what isn’t given."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.41:4.3"
msgid "Corā haranti rājāno,"
msgstr "Bandits take it, or rulers,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.41:4.4"
msgid "aggi ḍahati nassati."
msgstr "it’s consumed by fire, or lost."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.41:5.1"
msgid "Atha antena jahati,"
msgstr "Then in the end this corpse is cast off,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.41:5.2"
msgid "Sarīraṃ sapariggahaṃ;"
msgstr "along with all your possessions."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.41:5.3"
msgid "Etadaññāya medhāvī,"
msgstr "Knowing this, a clever person"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.41:5.4"
msgid "Bhuñjetha ca dadetha ca;"
msgstr "would enjoy what they have and also give it away."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.41:5.5"
msgid "Datvā ca bhutvā ca yathānubhāvaṃ,"
msgstr "After giving and using according to their means,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.41:5.6"
msgid "Anindito saggamupeti ṭhānan”ti."
msgstr "blameless, they go to a heavenly place.”"
